snippet: Game On Dude carried Chantel Sutherland to victory in the $500,000 Hollywood Gold Cup in Inglewood, Calif., making her the first female jockey to win the 73-year-old race.
abstract: Racehorse Game On Dude carries jockey Chantel Sutherland to victory in the $500,000 Hollywood Gold Cup in Inglewood, Calif, making her the first female jockey to win the 73-year-old race.
